We need to evaluate the quantity using the provided hint. Thus, \[
\begin{aligned}\binom{31}{28}& =\frac{31 !}{(31-28) !\,28!} \\ &=\frac{31\times 30\times 29 \times 28!}{28!\times 3\times 2\times 1} \\&=\frac{31\times 30\times 29}{3\times 2\times 1} \\ &=31\times 5\times 29=4695.\end{aligned}
\] The answer is: 4695.
